This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to analyze the semantic similarity of emoji. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with the intersection of computer science and linguistics. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the paper deals with sentiment analysis, which falls under the sub-category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
